          <Vi>ghi chú về nghi thức; quy định về nghi lễ</Vi>
          <En>A system of rules or procedures governing diplomatic or official occasions, especially regarding order of precedence and formal conduct.</En>
          <Example>The ambassador strictly adhered to diplomatic protocol during the state visit.</Example>
